metadata.name: gM mf34s
metadata.description:
34s will not solely be an art or collectible collection.  It is a long term study, an experiment, going against much of what was taught to me in this space over the past two years.  It is a collection of multiple series to help develop my craft, as as well as an opportunity to allow the art itself to engage and form community.

CC0... all of it.

Why 34s ... why not?

Ready for artistic experimentation, exploring different styles and embracing the culture.  All while testing open editions, limited editions & perceived rarity / value.

No roadmap, minimal rules.  I am the project ... WE will create it's path together.

_________________________

34s forever open edition pass.  

Collect [or] accumulate to use for future burn to redeem opportunities.  
__________________________
